{"word":"H2787 - חָרַר - chârar - khaw-rar' - Be angry","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָרַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chârar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-rar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be angry"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெந்துபோ, எரித்துப்போடு, வெந்திரு. வறண்டு போ. எரி, மூட்டு, கோபமாயிரு, காய்ந்துபோ, தகிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to burn, to be hot, to be scorched, to be charred"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be hot, to be scorched"},{"paragraph":"2) to burn, to be burned"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be scorched, to be burned"},{"paragraph":"2) to burn"},{"paragraph":"3) to be dry, to be angry"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pilpel) to cause to burn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>glow</i>, that is, literally (to <i>melt</i>, <i>burn</i>, <i>dry</i> up) or figuratively (to <i>show</i> or <i>incite passion</i>): - be angry, burn, dry, kindle."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2744 - חַרְחוּר - Charchûwr - khar-khoor'/2744\">H2744</a>, <a href=\"#/H2746 - חַרְחֻר - charchur - khar-khoor'/2746\">H2746</a>, <a href=\"#/H2787 - חָרַר - chârar - khaw-rar'/2787\">H2787</a>, <a href=\"#/H2788 - חָרֵר - chârêr - khaw-rare'/2788\">H2788</a>"}]}